VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT resource\s+"aws_cloudtrail"[^}]*enable_logging\s*=\s*false
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:enable_logging\s*=\s*false|is_logging\s*=\s*false|enabled\s*=\s*false && MISSING:# intentional|# cost|# development
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects CloudTrail configurations with logging explicitly disabled.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for CloudTrail Logging Disabled.
